# ArticleCalendarSection

## Purpose
A React Router archive route section that displays a navigable article calendar, filters articles by selected date through URL search parameters, and paginates results with `<Link>`.

**Semantic hints:** `calendar`, `schedule`, `dates`, `events-calendar`, `date-picker`, `archive`, `timeline`

Use on article archive routes, not inside individual article content.

## Props

| Prop | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `title` | `string` | Section title |
| `articles` | `Article[]` | All articles for the displayed month |
| `paginatedArticles` | `Article[]` | Articles visible on the current page |
| `currentPage` | `number` | Current pagination page |
| `totalPages` | `number` | Total number of pages |
| `pageSize` | `number` | Articles per page |
| `paginationBasePath` | `string` | React Router path used for pagination links |
| `id` | `string` | Section anchor ID. Defaults to `"calendar"` |
| `paginationHash` | `string` | Optional hash appended to pagination links |
| `selectedDate` | `Date` | Currently selected date |
| `onDateSelect` | `(date: Date) => void` | Called when a calendar day is selected |

